headline: Agoda Ranks Asia's Most Affordable Summer Destinations for Hoteliers to Manage Yields from Deals
summary: With value-driven travel gaining momentum across Asia, digital travel platform Agoda revealed its rankings of Asia's most affordable summer destinations led by Surabaya, Indonesia where average room rates are $35 per night*. This presents hoteliers with new opportunities to capture sustained demand and maximize returns even when offering competitive deals.
